    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for daily commuting. While the engine and transmission are in good working order, the exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches on the passenger side and a small dent in the rear bumper. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows some staining and wear on the driver's seat. All major electronics function properly, though the air conditioning takes a moment to reach full cooling capacity. This is a solid, honest car for someone prioritizing utility over aesthetics.",
